    <h3>Booking Protocols:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>A certified copy of ID and address, of the client, are needed</li>
        <li>The client must pay a deposit to secure their date and outfit</li>
        <li>On collection, client must sign a hire contract that includes all the terms and conditions</li>
        <li>The client's outstanding balance must be paid 3 weeks prior to the event</li>
        <li>If the item is not returned as per the contract, a money penalty will be added on the day and will  accumulate as time goes on</li>
        <li>If the item is lost, the company will keep the deposit and the client will pay for the remaining cost of the lost item.</li>
    </ul>
